  <p>Removing the liquid from a tank is one job; agitating and removing the settled sludge blanket from every compartment is a more thorough one. Both are useful, but they are not always the same service.</p>

  {/* Intended asset: /images/resources/septic-pumping-versus-septic-tank-cleaning-hero.webp — see public/images/resources/README.md */}
